008/**
009 * Ontology loader/parser exception.
010 *
011 * @author Samuel Kerrien (skerrien@ebi.ac.uk)
012 * @version $Id: OntologyLoaderException.java 656 2007-06-29 11:18:19 +0100 (Fri, 29 Jun 2007) skerrien $
013 * @since <pre>26-Apr-2006</pre>
014 */
015public class OntologyLoaderException extends Exception {
016    public OntologyLoaderException( String message ) {
017        super( message );
018    }
019
020    public OntologyLoaderException( String message, Throwable cause ) {
021        super( message, cause );
022    }
023}
